Cortex M4 - Quad Flat Package System of a Chip

ARM
bit - Smallest unit of information in binary
nibble - 4 bits of binary, 1 digit of hex.  0b1111 = 0xF  Max: 15
byte - 8 bits, 2 digits of hex                            Max: 255
halfword - 16 bits. 0x0CAD                                Max: 65,535
word - 32 bits.     0x00000CAD                            Max: 4,294,967,295
